  29     public class HorizontallyLess : Rel<int>
  30     {
  31         public nothrow HorizontallyLess() : diagram(null)
  32         {
  33         }
  34         public nothrow HorizontallyLess(Diagram* diagram_) : diagram(diagram_)
  35         {
  36         }
  37         public nothrow bool operator()(int leftIndex, int rightIndex) const
  38         {
  39             DiagramElement* left = diagram->GetElementByIndex(leftIndex);
  40             DiagramElement* right = diagram->GetElementByIndex(rightIndex);
  41             if (left->Location().x < right->Location().x)
  42             {
  43                 return true;
  44             }
  45             if (left->Location().x > right->Location().x)
  46             {
  47                 return false;
  48             }
  49             return left->Location().y < right->Location().y;
  50         }
  51         private Diagram* diagram;
  52     }

  92     public class DiagramElementFactory
  93     {
  94         static DiagramElementFactory() : instance(new DiagramElementFactory())
  95         {
  96         }
  97         public static DiagramElementFactory& Instance()
  98         {
  99             return *instance;
 100         }
 101         public DiagramElement* Create(const string& domElementName)
 102         {
 103             Map<string, DiagramElementCreator*>.ConstIterator it = registry.CFind(domElementName);
 104             if (it != registry.CEnd())
 105             {
 106                 DiagramElementCreator* creator = it->second;
 107                 return creator->Create();
 108             }
 109             else
 110             {
 111                 throw Exception("element '" + domElementName + "' not registered to diagram element factory");
 112             }
 113         }
 114         private DiagramElementFactory()
 115         {
 116             UniquePtr<DiagramElementCreator> classCreator(new ConcreteDiagramElementCreator<ClassElement>());
 117             registry["class"] = classCreator.Get();
 118             creators.Add(Rvalue(classCreator));
 119             UniquePtr<DiagramElementCreator> objectCreator(new ConcreteDiagramElementCreator<ObjectElement>());
 120             registry["object"] = objectCreator.Get();
 121             creators.Add(Rvalue(objectCreator));
 122             UniquePtr<DiagramElementCreator> noteCreator(new ConcreteDiagramElementCreator<NoteElement>());
 123             registry["note"] = noteCreator.Get();
 124             creators.Add(Rvalue(noteCreator));
 125             UniquePtr<DiagramElementCreator> relationshipCreator(new ConcreteDiagramElementCreator<RelationshipElement>());
 126             registry["relationship"] = relationshipCreator.Get();
 127             creators.Add(Rvalue(relationshipCreator));
 128         }
 129         private void Instantiate()
 130         {
 131             ConcreteDiagramElementCreator<ClassElement>().Create();
 132             ConcreteDiagramElementCreator<ObjectElement>().Create();
 133             ConcreteDiagramElementCreator<NoteElement>().Create();
 134             ConcreteDiagramElementCreator<RelationshipElement>().Create();
 135         }
 136         private static UniquePtr<DiagramElementFactory> instance;
 137         private List<UniquePtr<DiagramElementCreator>> creators;
 138         private Map<string, DiagramElementCreator*> registry;
 139     }

 141     public nothrow int MainDirection(DiagramElement* source, DiagramElement* target)
 142     {
 143         PointF sourceCenter = source->Center();
 144         PointF targetCenter = target->Center();
 145         Line line(sourceCenter, targetCenter);
 146         Vector v = line.ToVector();
 147         return MainDirection(v);
 148     }

 184         public void Save(const string& filePath)
 185         {
 186             StreamWriter writer = File.CreateText(filePath);
 187             CodeFormatter formatter(writer);
 188             formatter.SetIndentSize(1);
 189             System.Dom.Document diagramDocument;
 190             diagramDocument.AppendChild(UniquePtr<System.Dom.Node>(new System.Dom.Element(u"diagram")));
 191             HashMap<ContainerElement*, int> containerElementIndexMap;
 192             List<ContainerElement*> containerElements;
 193             List<RelationshipElement*> relationshipElements;
 194             for (UniquePtr<DiagramElement>& element : elements)
 195             {
 196                 if (element.Get() is ContainerElement*)
 197                 {
 198                     containerElements.Add(cast<ContainerElement*>(element.Get()));
 199                 }
 200                 else if (element.Get() is RelationshipElement*)
 201                 {
 202                     relationshipElements.Add(cast<RelationshipElement*>(element.Get()));
 203                 }
 204             }
 205             int nc = cast<int>(containerElements.Count());
 206             for (int i = 0; i < nc; ++i;)
 207             {
 208                 ContainerElement* containerElement = containerElements[i];
 209                 containerElementIndexMap[containerElement] = i;
 210                 UniquePtr<System.Dom.Element> domElement = containerElement->CreateDomElement();
 211                 containerElement->Write(domElement.Get());
 212                 diagramDocument.DocumentElement()->AppendChild(UniquePtr<System.Dom.Node>(domElement.Release()));
 213             }
 214             int nr = cast<int>(relationshipElements.Count());
 215             for (int i = 0; i < nr; ++i;)
 216             {
 217                 RelationshipElement* relationshipElement = relationshipElements[i];
 218                 relationshipElement->SetContainerElementIndeces(containerElementIndexMap);
 219                 UniquePtr<System.Dom.Element> domElement = relationshipElement->CreateDomElement();
 220                 relationshipElement->Write(domElement.Get());
 221                 diagramDocument.DocumentElement()->AppendChild(UniquePtr<System.Dom.Node>(domElement.Release()));
 222             }
 223             diagramDocument.Write(formatter);
 224         }
 225         public void Load(const string& filePath)
 226         {
 227             List<DiagramElement*> relationshipElements;
 228             UniquePtr<System.Dom.Document> diagramDocument = System.Dom.ReadDocument(filePath);
 229             UniquePtr<XPathObject> result = Evaluate(u"/diagram/*", diagramDocument.Get());
 230             if (!result.IsNull())
 231             {
 232                 if (result.Get() is XPathNodeSet*)
 233                 {
 234                     XPathNodeSet* nodeSet = cast<XPathNodeSet*>(result.Get());
 235                     int n = nodeSet->Length();
 236                     for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i;)
 237                     {
 238                         System.Dom.Node* node = (*nodeSet)[i];
 239                         if (node is System.Dom.Element*)
 240                         {
 241                             System.Dom.Element* element = cast<System.Dom.Element*>(node);
 242                             string domElementName = ToUtf8(element->Name());
 243                             UniquePtr<DiagramElement> diagramElement(DiagramElementFactory.Instance().Create(domElementName));
 244                             diagramElement->SetDiagram(this);
 245                             diagramElement->Read(element);
 246                             if (diagramElement.Get() is RelationshipElement*)
 247                             {
 248                                 relationshipElements.Add(diagramElement.Get());
 249                             }
 250                             AddElement(diagramElement.Release());
 251                         }
 252                     }
 253                 }
 254             }
 255             for (DiagramElement* relationshipElement : relationshipElements)
 256             {
 257                 relationshipElement->Resolve();
 258             }
 259         }

 286         public void Draw(Graphics& graphics)
 287         {
 288             if (Changed())
 289             {
 290                 ResetChanged();
 291                 if (layout == null)
 292                 {
 293                     layoutPtr.Reset(new Layout(graphics));
 294                     layout = layoutPtr.Get();
 295                 }
 296                 for (const UniquePtr<DiagramElement>& element : elements)
 297                 {
 298                     element->Measure(graphics, *layout);
 299                 }
 300             }
 301             if (Invalidated())
 302             {
 303                 ResetInvalidated();
 304             }
 305             List<DiagramElement*> relationshipElements;
 306             for (const UniquePtr<DiagramElement>& element : elements)
 307             {
 308                 if (element.Get() is ContainerElement*)
 309                 {
 310                     element->Draw(graphics, *layout);
 311                 }
 312                 else if (element.Get() is RelationshipElement*)
 313                 {
 314                     relationshipElements.Add(element.Get());
 315                 }
 316             }
 317             for (DiagramElement* relationshipElement : relationshipElements)
 318             {
 319                 relationshipElement->Draw(graphics, *layout);
 320             }
 321             operation->Draw(graphics, *layout);
 322             selection->Draw(graphics);
 323         }

 413         public nothrow bool HasIntersectingContrainerElements(const RectF& rect) const

 523         public void Paste(const ustring& clipboardData)
 524         {
 525             UniquePtr<AddElementsCommand> addElementsCommand(new AddElementsCommand(*this));
 526             UniquePtr<System.Dom.Document> diagramElementDoc = System.Dom.ParseDocument(clipboardData, "clipboard");
 527             UniquePtr<XPathObject> result = Evaluate(u"/spring.diagram.elements/*", diagramElementDoc.Get());
 528             if (!result.IsNull())
 529             {
 530                 if (result.Get() is XPathNodeSet*)
 531                 {
 532                     XPathNodeSet* nodeSet = cast<XPathNodeSet*>(result.Get());
 533                     UniquePtr<ElementSelection> elementSelection(new ElementSelection(*this));
 534                     List<RelationshipElement*> relationshipElements;
 535                     HashMap<int, int> indexMap;
 536                     int n = nodeSet->Length();
 537                     for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i;)
 538                     {
 539                         System.Dom.Node* node = (*nodeSet)[i];
 540                         if (node is System.Dom.Element*)
 541                         {
 542                             System.Dom.Element* element = cast<System.Dom.Element*>(node);
 543                             string domElementName = ToUtf8(element->Name());
 544                             UniquePtr<DiagramElement> diagramElement(DiagramElementFactory.Instance().Create(domElementName));
 545                             diagramElement->Read(element);
 546                             int index = elements.Count();
 547                             if (diagramElement.Get() is RelationshipElement*)
 548                             {
 549                                 relationshipElements.Add(cast<RelationshipElement*>(diagramElement.Get()));
 550                             }
 551                             AddElement(diagramElement.Release());
 552                             indexMap[i] = index;
 553                             elementSelection->Add(index);
 554                             addElementsCommand->AddIndex(index);
 555                         }
 556                     }
 557                     for (RelationshipElement* relationship : relationshipElements)
 558                     {
 559                         relationship->MapIndeces(indexMap);
 560                         relationship->Resolve();
 561                     }
 562                     SetSelection(elementSelection.Release());

1005         public nothrow string ToString() const

1013         public inline constexpr nothrow int ToInt() const

1016         }
1017         public nothrow PointF Calculate(const PointF& point, float w, int index, int count)
1018         {
1019             int s = ToInt();
1020             switch (s)
1021             {
1022                 case TopLeft():
1023                 case BottomLeft():
1024                 {
1025                     return PointF(point.x + index * w, point.y);
1026                 }
1027                 case TopRight():
1028                 case BottomRight():
1029                 {
1030                     return PointF(point.x - index * w, point.y);
1031                 }
1032                 case LeftTop():
1033                 case RightTop():
1034                 {
1035                     return PointF(point.x, point.y + index * w);
1036                 }
1037                 case LeftBottom():
1038                 case RightBottom():
1039                 {
1040                     return PointF(point.x, point.y - index * w);
1041                 }
1042                 case LeftCenter():
1043                 case RightCenter():
1044                 {
1045                     if ((count & 1) == 0)
1046                     {
1047                         return PointF(point.x, point.y - (count / 2) * w + index * w + w / 2);
1048                     }
1049                     else
1050                     {
1051                         return PointF(point.x, point.y - (count / 2) * w + index * w);
1052                     }
1053                 }
1054                 case TopCenter():
1055                 case BottomCenter():
1056                 {
1057                     if ((count & 1) == 0)
1058                     {
1059                         return PointF(point.x - (count / 2) * w + index * w + w / 2, point.y);
1060                     }
1061                     else
1062                     {
1063                         return PointF(point.x - (count / 2) * w + index * w, point.y);
1064                     }
1065                 }
1066             }
1067             return PointF();
1068         }

1070         public SnapPoint secondaryPoint;
1071     }

1073     public nothrow Snap ParseSnap(const string& str)
1074     {
1075         List<string> components = str.Split(".");
1076         if (components.Count() == 2)
1077         {
1078             SnapPoint primary = ParseSnapPoint(components[0]);
1079             if (primary == SnapPoint.operation || primary == SnapPoint.field)
1080             {
1081                 Snap snap(primary, cast<SnapPoint>(ParseSByte(components[1])));
1082                 return snap;
1083             }
1084             else
1085             {
1086                 Snap snap(primary, ParseSnapPoint(components[1]));
1087                 return snap;
1088             }
1089         }
1090         return Snap();
1091     }

1380         public nothrow int MainDirection() const
1381         {
1382             if (sourceEndpoints.IsEmpty())
1383             {
1384                 if (source.element != null && target.element != null)
1385                 {
1386                     return MainDirection(source.element, target.element);
1387                 }
1388             }
1389             else if (target.element != null)
1390             {
1391                 LogView* log = Application.GetLogView();
1392                 Map<int, int> directionMap;
1393                 for (const Endpoint& sourceEndpoint : sourceEndpoints)
1394                 {
1395                     if (sourceEndpoint.element != null)
1396                     {
1397                         Line line(target.element->Center(), sourceEndpoint.element->Center());
1398                         Vector v = line.ToVector();
1399                         if (v.x > 0) ++directionMap[180];
1400                         if (v.y > 0) ++directionMap[270];
1401                         if (v.x < 0) ++directionMap[0];
1402                         if (v.y < 0) ++directionMap[90];
1403                     }
1404                 }
1405                 List<Pair<int, int>> directionList;
1406                 for (const Pair<int, int>& p : directionMap)
1407                 {
1408                     directionList.Add(p);
1409                 }
1410                 Sort(directionList.Begin(), directionList.End(), DecreasingOrderBySecond());
1411                 Pair<int, int> max = directionList.Front();
1412                 if (log != null)
1413                 {
1414                     log->WriteLine("MainDirection: " + ToString(max.first) + ", " + ToString(max.second));
1415                 }
1416                 return max.first;
1417             }
1418             return 0;
1419         }

1433         public nothrow void Straighten()
1434         {
1435             if (!intermediatePoints.IsEmpty())
1436             {
1437                 PointF prev = source.point;
1438                 for (PointF& next : intermediatePoints)
1439                 {
1440                     Line line(prev, next);
1441                     Vector v(line.ToVector());

1443                     {
1444                         case 0:
1445                         case 180:
1446                         {
1447                             next.y = prev.y;
1448                             break;
1449                         }
1450                         case 90:
1451                         case 270:
1452                         {
1453                             next.x = prev.x;
1454                             break;
1455                         }
1456                     }

1458                 }
1459                 if (!intermediatePoints.IsEmpty())
1460                 {

1462                     Line line(last, target.point);

1465                     {

1517                                 target.element->Offset(0.0f, dy);

1598         public nothrow bool Contains(const PointF& from, const PointF& to, const PointF& loc, float selectedLineWidth)
1599         {

3400         private bool IsHorizontalLine(const PointF& prev, const PointF& next, Line& textLine)
3401         {
3402             Line line(prev, next);
3403             Vector v = line.ToVector();
3404             int direction = MainDirection(v);
3405             if (direction == 0)
3406             {
3407                 textLine = line;
3408                 return true;
3409             }
3410             else if (direction == 180)

3417         private void DrawSourceText(Graphics& graphics, const Font& font, const Brush& textBrush, const Line& line, float leadingWidth)
3418         {

3420             {
3421                 GraphicsState state = graphics.SaveChecked();
3422                 graphics.TranslateTransformChecked(0, -sourceTextSize.h, MatrixOrder.append);
3423                 float dx = line.end.x - line.start.x;
3424                 float dy = line.end.y - line.start.y;
3425                 if (Abs(dy) >= Epsilon() * 2 && Abs(dx) >= Epsilon() * 2)
3426                 {
3427                     float length = cast<float>(Sqrt(dx * dx, dy * dy));
3428                     dx = dx / length;
3429                     dy = dy / length;
3430                     float angle = cast<float>(180.0 * Atan2(dy, dx) / PI());
3431                     graphics.RotateTransformChecked(angle, MatrixOrder.append);
3432                 }
3433                 graphics.TranslateTransformChecked(line.start.x + leadingWidth, line.start.y, MatrixOrder.append);
3434                 graphics.DrawStringChecked(source.text, font, PointF(0, 0), textBrush);
